OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,FThe price of diesel has hit almost #2
OL,7,Fa litre in parts of the south,
OL,8,Fmatching the previous record high of
OL,9,F2022, and experts say it's possible
OL,10,Fprices could rise even further.
OL,12,FITV News found diesel at #1.99 at
OL,13,FChieveley Services on the A34 in
OL,14,FBerkshire and on the Isle of Wight,
OL,15,Fand petrol as high as #1.80 a litre.
OL,17,FBut many say it couldn't have come at
OL,18,Fa worse time as millions of people set
OL,19,Foff this week for the Easter bank
OL,20,Fholiday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
