PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,FBusinesses also say the soaring cost
OL,7,Fof fuel because of the Middle East
OL,8,Fconflict is causing their profits to
OL,9,Fplummet.
OL,11,FIce cream vendor and manufacturer
OL,12,FTombaccini Raniero works in Winchester
OL,13,Fand says the rise is having a bad
OL,14,Fimpact on his business.
OL,16,FFuel to run his vans has increased and
OL,17,Fso has the cost of the ice cream from
OL,18,FItaly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,F"The fact our own vans go out on the
OL,7,Fstreet that is for us the fuel
OL,8,Fincrease is having a big impact," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"We are simply not able to go out as
OL,12,Fmuch as we used to because it is not
OL,13,Fcost affective.
OL,15,F"A lot of the customers we have are
OL,16,Faffected because they have old vans
OL,17,Fand they consume quite a lot of fuel.
OL,19,F"Our sales of ice cream are much lower
OL,20,Fthan they used to be."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
