PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,FToto Mazloom runs an ice cream company
OL,7,Fin Sandhurst and has described similar
OL,8,Fissues.
OL,10,FHe has ten vans covering licensed
OL,11,Fpitches in Surrey and Hampshire and
OL,12,Fsays he's alarmed by rising prices.
OL,14,F"A full tank usually cost me around
OL,15,F#100, but now it's about #135,
OL,16,Fdepending obviously which petrol
OL,17,Fstation we go to, but it's a
OL,18,Fnightmare," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,F"We have to keep the vans running when
OL,7,Fwe're serving and obviously they're
OL,8,Fall diesel powered.
OL,10,F"So with that in mind, we'll go
OL,11,Fthrough a lot of fuel and having 10
OL,12,Fvans and 33% increase across each van
OL,13,Fis a nightmare."
OL,15,FMr Mazloom says the last time fuel
OL,16,Frose to these levels they had to close
OL,17,Fearly in the season.
OL,19,FTaxi driver Paul Jeneway has also felt
OL,20,Fthe impact of the rising cost of fuel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
