OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, he said: "We
OL,7,Fcan't change the fares because we run
OL,8,Fby meters.
OL,10,F"So the fares have the be the same all
OL,11,Fthe time, you have to carry on with it
OL,12,Fand can't do anything about it."
OL,14,FAcross the country the average diesel
OL,15,Fprice is 182.8p a litre, which is up
OL,16,F40p since the start of the conflict,
OL,17,Fand for unleaded the average is 152.8p
OL,18,Fa litre - that's up 20p.
OL,20,FIt means it now costs more than #100
OL,21,Fto fill a family car.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
