FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,FThe government gets increased vat when
OL,7,Ffuel prices go up. That's estimated at
OL,8,F20 million pounds a day more because
OL,9,Fof the current crisis.
OL,11,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Business
OL,12,FSecretary Peter Kyle said the
OL,13,Fgovernment is in "constant touch with
OL,14,Fpeople who are representing the
OL,15,Faviation sectors and also the motoring
OL,16,Fsectors."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,F"The AA and also the body, the trade
OL,7,Fbody representing the aviation sectors
OL,8,Fhave both said that there is enough
OL,9,Fsupply in the supply chains for fuel
OL,10,Ffor the immediate period," he said.
OL,12,F"So in other words they are
OL,13,Fencouraging people to go about life as
OL,14,Fnormal and we as a government are
OL,15,Fsaying go about life as normal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
