PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775131865
OL,3,CDiesel hits #2 a litre as experts warn
OL,4,Cprices could rise even further
OL,6,F"If this changes, because we are in
OL,7,Fvery very close touch and we have very
OL,8,Fvery good knowledge of the supply
OL,9,Fchains, if this changes we will be
OL,10,Fupfront and honest with the public
OL,11,Fabout the adaptations but we're doing
OL,12,Feverything we can to build resilience
OL,13,Finto the system."
